questions.question_name:
XXXXX is conducting market research on behalf of our client concerning certain new products and product ideas for the discussion in which you have agreed to participate.In the course of the Market Research, the Agency will disclose to you certain confidential and proprietary information.

The Confidential Information may include, for example, the features, characteristics, look, feel, taste and image of the products and product ideas that the Agency will present to you in the course of the Market Research.

Additionally, as part of the research, during your session, you will be video and/or audio recorded. These recordings will be used by and the company commissioning the research for market research purposes only. Anything you say will be treated confidentially. At no time, will your details be passed on to a third party.

By Agreement, you acknowledge and agree:

· to hold all Confidential Information in strict confidence and to refrain from using any Confidential Information for your own or any third party’s benefit, or in any other manner;

· not to disclose to any third party that our client is interested in the subject matter of the Market Research; and

· that said client is the proprietary owner of the products and product ideas subject of the Market Research and that you have no indirect or direct right or title therein or thereto

If you agree to participate, you will receive AU$150 in appreciation for your time and opinions.

Is this something you are willing and able to do?

questions.question_name:
Based on your answers, you sound exactly like the type of person we’d like to include in our study! I’d like to invite you to participate in the upcoming 60-minute interview. The conversation would be at your home, so it’s more informal and comfortable.

There are a few key things that are needed to make your participation a success. Please review the following information carefully.

Your participation takes place online. Please confirm that you can meet the following technical specifications:

• You will be using a laptop or desktop computer

• You have, or are willing to install, Chrome or Firefox as your browser for the session

• You have a working webcam that is either built in or attached to your computer/laptop.

• In addition to accessing by computer, at the same time you might also need to be called into a conference line using a mobile phone or landline.

• You will need to be able to participate uninterrupted, and from a quiet place.

Are you still willing to participate in our study?
